metadata.name: Solitary
metadata.description:
This shot was captured in the south of Italy in September 2021.
Everything in this moment came together to create one of my most loved and cherished photos.
Nothing of this shoot was planned. Everything happened naturally and spontaneously, adding to the magic of the photo.

JPG  ||  5003× 6254 px  ||  20.9 MB
